Detailed Description

template<typename T, typename InterfaceType>
struct viennamath::expression_traits< rt_constant< T, InterfaceType > >

Specialization of the expression traits system: A runtime constant does not allow for copying, otherwise one runs into problems with tempories.

Note: There seems to be a minor design flaw here, because the return type does not provide what the name suggests. This will be improved in one of the future releases.
